{"tid":1462700,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"凡是敵人反對的都要擁護","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:11:09.000Z","uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe941a41644e62381e38adcb7fd7bf57426df80","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"p牌第一次發文。<br />\n睇唔過睇次次有夢發都係一堆散水post，叫人唔好呢樣唔好果樣<br />\n<br />\n<strong>麻煩大家擘大對眼睇清楚</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢個係好明顯既徵兆，前線係做緊對家唔想你做既野</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁先應該繼續啊！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我提議你心底可以有新rule:<br />\n如果熱門第一頁有5個以上無FC既「聽講」post, 「意見」post, 根本唔需要再睇同類意見<br />\n（包括呢個）"},{"pid":"70ca6111d1f6b2977d4b6caf9781aa6aeb931c14","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"自推十次1"},{"pid":"a019832b30fd8a025ce3c5aa713369c1f547da05","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:08:20.000Z","msg":"自推十次2"},{"pid":"a6decda253cf3998b721892e0a996c38bf894e0e","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"自推十次3"},{"pid":"548b0d31200bb0f0fcec471af0308248fdfe1263","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:17.000Z","msg":"自推十次4"},{"pid":"be57510796a3095decb1ec4e5604f51bc8ec8824","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"自推十次5"},{"pid":"4b0138639335879871bee4ac62e15c160a7261d1","tid":1462700,"uid":277582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"自推十次6"},{"pid":"945